      "span_text": "This effect is also expected because of the switch in language dominance of minority in majority language after the age of 8 Pfaff 1999), the brain development activity in left temporal and frontal areas in normal reading and the increase in using the semantic pathway in the fluent reading stage, as described in the introduction."
